Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.58,0:02:19.75,Thought,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,This was probably the right decision to take, compared to running away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:24.79,Thought,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I might have made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:31.04,Thought,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Because her body was really, almost unbelievably light.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:32.08,Thought,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:38.30,Thought,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Senjyogahara... she doesn't seem to actually weigh anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:54.61,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cultural festival, but we're already in our third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:59.36,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,We don't really need to do anything,\N and exams preparations are more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:03.16,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we narrow down the options first,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:07.37,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,before we let the rest vote on what we'll do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:08.79,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds great, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:11.16,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,It seems democratic at first glance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.16,0:03:14.92,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,You're as sarcastic as ever, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:16.88,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say that you're quirky?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.69,0:03:25.21,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Hanekawa Tsubasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:26.97,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Our class president.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:31.52,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Always prim and proper, always follows the rules, terribly serious, and well liked by the teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.65,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,The class president of class presidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:41.03,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,As a reference, Araragi-kun, what did you do for the cultural festival the last two years?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:43.16,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Haunted house and café.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:51.71,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm discussing the plans for the cultural festival with Hanekawa, the president of the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:56.67,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't there a girl called Senjyogahara in our class?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:58.83,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Senjyogahara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:01.60,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.80,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm a bit curious about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:06.82,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she sickly and often absent from school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.82,0:04:09.42,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she'll attend the cultural festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:15.93,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, look, the name "Senjyogahara Hitagi" is pretty unusual and interesting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:18.81,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Senjyogahara based on the name of a place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:20.98,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I wasn't talking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:23.83,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking more about her given name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.83,0:04:27.63,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Senjyogahara-san's given name is Hitagi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:29.69,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Is that strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.69,0:04:33.76,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly, Hitagi is a term used in civil engineering.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:35.70,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,You know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:37.68,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:39.13,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,I just happen to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:53.07,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:53.85,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:57.31,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,...for you to be curious about someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.64,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:02.90,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Boys always like sickly girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:05.78,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh gosh, how disgusting, how disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:08.95,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Sickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:14.16,Thought,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,But... was that really caused by an illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.97,0:05:17.87,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what kind of person is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:22.88,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,You probably know more about her than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:25.76,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't she in your class for three consecutive years?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:29.26,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, now that you remind me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:38.23,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she's the perfect model student.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.26,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Her grades are good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:41.36,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:45.56,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,But I've only been in the same class as her for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:47.81,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't really know her that well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:50.20,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,That month included Golden Week, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:52.08,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Week, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:55.11,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Did something happen during Golden Week?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.11,0:05:57.11,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing. Please continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:05:59.33,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:02.99,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't talk much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:04.76,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't seem to have any friends either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:07.72,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's probably because of an illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:12.80,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,She was a much more active and cheerful girl back in junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:17.98,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,You were in the same school as her during junior high?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:18.69,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:25.01,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Senjyogahara-san was really pretty, and she was good at sports, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:26.69,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,She was the star of the athletics club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:32.48,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've heard a lot of rumors about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:33.41,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:37.62,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Rumors saying that she's very sociable and a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:41.85,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,There are also rumors that she's not at all snobby,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:46.89,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,even though her father is a big shot in a\N foreign company and lives in a mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:49.08,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,She sounds like Wonder Woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:50.13,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:53.85,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't be saying this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:56.10,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,but Senjyogahara-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:57.47,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:07:03.48,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,She looks a lot prettier the way she is now, compared to the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:08.49,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Her presence is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.28,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,very ephemeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:14.57,Thought,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,An ephemeral presence...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:22.06,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I just remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:24.15,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Oshino is looking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:26.68,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Oshino-San? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.71,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he needs some help with his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:32.45,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Hadekawa, can I leave the rest to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:36.25,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay, provided you promise to make up for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:39.29,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't appropriate to make Oshino-san wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:39.84,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:43.49,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Give my regards to Oshino-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:51.14,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,What were you discussing with Hanekawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:56.24,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:01.29,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,My mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:05.67,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,The correct way to say it is, "You can move, but it's very dangerous."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:09.59,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Things like curiosity really resemble cockroaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:13.25,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,They just hang around, intruding on secrets that people want to keep private.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:14.80,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's so depressing I can't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.27,0:08:18.18,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.46,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:21.38,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Is your right cheek feeling lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:23.77,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,You could have just told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:29.02,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,I was careless, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:30.32,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect that someone would...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:36.20,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,drop a banana peel in a place like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:38.76,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,You noticed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:39.37,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:41.54,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:43.54,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,any weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:49.32,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, it's not as if I'm completely weightless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:51.30,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Someone with my height and build
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:55.38,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,should weigh a little over 45kg on average.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:57.72,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,But my actual weight is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:00.56,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,5kg.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:05.85,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,It happened after I graduated from junior high, before I entered this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:10.06,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,I met a crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:12.33,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,It took my weight away almost completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:17.00,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you don't really need to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:21.90,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just telling you about it because you'll cause me a lot of trouble if you continue snooping around, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.69,0:09:23.87,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Araragi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:28.75,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Araragi Koyomi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:31.17,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:36.05,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,to ensure that you'll keep my secret to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:39.68,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do for myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:44.73,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,How should I seal your mouth so that you'll swear not to reveal my secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:46.94,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,even if your mouth is ripped apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:51.65,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, all I want is for you to remain silent and seem indifferent to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:58.75,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Nod your head twice, if you're willing to promise that you'll remain silent and seem indifferent, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:02.28,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat any other actions you take as hostility
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:04.87,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,and attack you immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:08.02,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:09.12,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:21.88,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:22.68,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,That's splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:26.24,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you go this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:27.02,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:33.65,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Araragi-kun, remember to ignore me properly from tomorrow onward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:35.32,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:44.83,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,She's like a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:51.81,Thought,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,But it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:54.10,Thought,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be all right despite an injury like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:55.75,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:57.17,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Araragi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.61,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Hanekawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:10:59.88,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,You're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:02.92,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be rushing over to Oshino-san's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:05.17,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Hanekawa, do you like bananas?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:05.94,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:08.69,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really hate them, because they're nutritious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:11.44,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,If I have to say whether I like or hate them...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:13.07,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess I like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:15.94,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you like them, you must not eat them in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:17.44,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:19.39,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Just eating them is still okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:23.77,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,but I absolutely won't forgive you if you toss them away carelessly on the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:26.64,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Araragi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:28.45,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Araragi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:30.14,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run in the corridor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:35.71,Default,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll report you to the teachers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:49.26,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.26,0:11:52.97,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I should be more honest and say that I'm shocked to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:58.59,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,You were able to rekindle your rebellious spirit so quickly, despite your ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:11:59.60,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Senjyogahara—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:01.11,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:02.65,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:08.02,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's commence our war.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:09.29,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're mistaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:10.91,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not here for a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.67,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,No war?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:13.48,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,How disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:16.81,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Then what {\i1}are{i0\fscx120} {\r}you here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:21.63,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a chance, but I think I might be able to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:22.59,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:25.46,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Stop joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:27.55,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:30.97,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep quiet and seem indifferent towards me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:33.94,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat kindness as hostility.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:47.45,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Your wound...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:50.66,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,has vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:54.91,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,What... happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:56.95,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oshino?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.95,0:12:58.00,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oshino-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:00.09,Default,Kiyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, he's called Oshino Meme.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:02.19,Default,Kiyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Oshino,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:04.11,Default,Kiyomi,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to change back from a vampire to a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:08.09,Default,Kiyomi,0000,0000,0000,,But there are still after-effects from having an immortal body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:11.09,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,708)}Oshino Meme?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:14.06,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,708)}Sounds like quite a moe name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:16.97,Default,Kiyomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,708)}Don't expect him to be anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:19.52,Default,Kiyomi,0000,0000,0000,,He's a middle-aged man well past his thirties.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:20.86,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:24.28,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,But he must have had moe characteristics when he was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:27.53,Default,Kiyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at real humans that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:30.53,Default,Kiyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you're familiar with terms like "moe" and "characteristics"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:33.57,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,They're part of a general education.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:36.91,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,People with characteristics like mine are called tsundere, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:40.92,Thought,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,People with characteristics like yours are more like tundras.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:54.21,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,My butt hurts and feels numb.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:13:56.34,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,My skirt is crumpled, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:13:57.69,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Not my responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:13:59.80,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Stop making excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:00.69,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cut it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:02.82,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Which part are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:11.82,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, where's your bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:12.99,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,You're empty-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:15.69,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,I left my textbook in my school locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:20.03,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't need a bag if I stuff school supplies around my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:21.77,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:26.26,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't have both my hands free,\N it's hard to fight when the moment demands it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:30.21,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Leave your school supplies and stuff with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:31.11,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:32.27,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Hand them over. I'll keep them locked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:39.18,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Oshino is my savior, even though he's a weird old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.18,0:14:42.67,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let a dangerous person see my savior,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:44.06,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,so give me your school supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.41,0:14:48.07,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you saying that, after we've come all the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:50.82,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you intend to deceive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:57.20,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Very well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.73,0:14:58.75,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.54,0:15:05.71,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:07.80,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:11.18,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't lowered my guard against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:14.05,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "you haven't lowered your guard"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:15.20,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:20.05,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Five thousand of my rowdy comrades will proceed forthwith to invade your home
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:22.80,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,if I fail to contact them once a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.80,0:15:24.15,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.87,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about such unnecessary details.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.87,0:15:28.05,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you can finish me off in a minute?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:29.69,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that I'm a certain boxer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:34.78,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Both your younger sisters are still in junior high, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:49.30,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:50.19,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:52.01,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't expect me to thank you for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:53.80,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.64,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, you should be thanking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:57.04,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:16:01.79,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,I purposely stapled the inside of your cheek, instead of the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:04.34,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,so that the injury wouldn't be obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:09.39,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the same as when a mugger says, "Let's hit his stomach instead of his head so the injury won't be obvious"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:13.21,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, my worries were all for naught.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.21,0:16:14.36,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:17.99,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Would you feel hurt if I said that\N an immortal body is pretty convenient?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:20.11,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel that way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:21.59,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.59,0:16:23.37,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm no longer immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:25.80,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,I just recover from injuries very quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:27.38,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Other than that, I'm a normal human.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:31.66,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Araragi-kun, let me say one final thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.66,0:16:32.73,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:35.90,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,You probably can't tell when I'm clothed,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:40.64,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not worth violating the law in order to possess my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:43.31,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:46.13,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,On the whole, you seem a bit excessively self-conscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:48.23,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,or should I say that you have an exceedingly strong persecution complex?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:49.76,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:52.57,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's true, there are things that you should and shouldn't say, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.49,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,You're aware of it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:17:01.34,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Putting that aside, does this Oshino fellow\N actually live in such a broken-down building?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.34,0:17:04.62,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's quite a weird person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:08.54,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,But he's an expert when it comes to people like you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:12.24,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Araragi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:13.67,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:19.12,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Araragi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:21.81,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,Today, you've brought a different girl here yet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:22.92,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:24.85,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me sound like a cheap character.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:28.47,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.47,0:17:29.31,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Oshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:30.70,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:32.72,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Senjyogahara Hitagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:37.86,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Araragi-kun's classmate, and he's told me about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:40.03,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:41.34,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Oshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:42.51,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Two years ago, she—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:44.52,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me "she."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:46.37,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Then what should I call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:48.12,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Senjyogahara-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:51.45,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Senjyogahara-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:54.01,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it so monotonously.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:55.05,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Pronounce it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:56.89,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Senjyogahara-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:59.21,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:00.37,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,You might've blinded me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:01.68,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you were rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:03.51,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of equivalent exchange is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:08.14,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,40 grams of bronze, 25 grams of zinc, 15 grams of nickel, and 5 grams of embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:12.06,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,I added 97 kilograms of malice and transmuted them into the earlier rash remark.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:13.73,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't most of it malice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:15.90,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I was lying about the embarrassment bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:18.40,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,The most important element that shouldn't be omitted was omitted!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:21.17,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, first things first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.17,0:18:23.66,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:26.74,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, ignore her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:28.08,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,She's without shadow or form.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:29.83,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,She's without a name and therefore has no reason to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:30.71,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,That's what she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:32.68,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:34.80,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,I gave her a name yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:37.26,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,After all, because of her I worked a lot during Golden Week.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:39.63,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she has a name now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:40.47,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,What did you name her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.88,0:18:43.05,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,I named her Oshino Shinobu:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:45.64,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,Heart under blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:47.65,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,The name fits her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.65,0:18:50.06,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,I just let her use my surname.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.06,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:54.59,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,As I was asking earlier, what happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:56.94,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you that nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:18:59.11,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,A ruined vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:01.16,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,The remaining scraps of a beautiful ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:03.78,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I say, her current state was inevitable, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:04.87,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:07.41,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay if nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:11.00,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you can help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:12.35,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,Help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:13.90,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:16.67,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,My dear, you are the only one who can save yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:21.61,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Before now, five people have said the same thing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.61,0:19:23.39,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,All of them were charlatans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:26.93,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you one of them, Oshino-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:31.38,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,My dear, you seem to be quite energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:33.40,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see something nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:38.07,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,We can't continue this conversation unless you tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:40.03,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,I'll guard your secret strictly. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:43.82,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I'll do a simple explanation first—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:45.64,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:47.07,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain it to him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:48.41,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Senjyogahara...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:51.46,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:58.30,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Omoshikani literally means "weight crab."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:55.92,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,Omoshikani.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.52,0:19:58.30,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Omoshikani?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:19:59.42,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:02.80,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,It's a common folk-tale in the mountainous region of Kyushu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:07.15,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on the area, it's called Omoshikani, Omoishikani, Omoshigani,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.15,0:20:09.68,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,and sometimes even Omoishikami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.15,0:20:11.56,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Note: In Japanese, crab is "kani" and god is "kami."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:11.56,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,They say that crab and gods are related.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.99,0:20:14.65,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,But why does it appear in Kyushu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:17.93,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,The location is meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:20.35,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,It will appear when the conditions are met.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:21.36,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:27.19,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,There are stories where it takes the form of a rabbit instead of a crab in this kind of situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:31.54,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,There are even stories where it takes the form of a beautiful woman, though not as pretty as Shinobu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:34.21,Default,Koyomi,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like the patterns on the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:39.13,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the young lady here encountered a crab, so it's a crab this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:41.09,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you say all of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.77,0:20:44.72,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what it's called.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.89,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,Names are important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:50.95,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,I already said earlier that it might not be a crab and might instead be a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:54.65,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,An Omoshikani derived from an Omoishikami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:57.98,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my dear, you can be considered as the luckiest among the unlucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:20:59.73,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:02.79,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,Because gods exist everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:05.32,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,They are everywhere, yet nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:08.41,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,My dear, I can say that it might've existed around you before you became like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:10.26,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,or it might possibly never have existed around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.46,0:21:13.76,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like a Zen riddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:16.55,Note,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Shugendou is an ancient Japanese religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:16.55,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,It's Shinto, or more accurately Shugendou.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.55,0:21:18.34,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be mistaken, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:20.67,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't end up like this because of a specific event.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:22.63,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that your point of view deviated a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:24.49,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,My point of view?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.49,0:21:25.72,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:29.21,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,My dear, it pisses me off to see you act as if you're the victim here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.66,0:21:36.72,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.72,0:21:38.13,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:41.04,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,I thought for sure that you were just a selfish young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:43.51,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.51,0:21:47.69,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,Because most people who encounter Omoshikani are like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.69,0:21:49.71,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,You don't encounter them just because you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:51.31,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,They're gods and don't normally interfere with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.48,0:21:54.08,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:57.14,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,They're just there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.14,0:21:59.88,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,My dear, they won't appear unless you desire something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.85,0:22:05.13,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I didn't originally plan to get so involved in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:07.95,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,But okay, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.95,0:22:11.05,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you if you want to get your weight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.71,0:22:13.48,Default,Meme,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Araragi-kun introduced you to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.76,0:22:17.60,Default,Hitagi,0000,0000,0000,,You'll help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.84,0:23:56.60,Avoid Preview Text,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.60,0:23:57.01,Avoid Preview Text,Tsukihi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tsukihi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.01,0:23:58.62,Avoid Preview Text,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for the preview segment quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.84,0:23:58.62,Avoid Preview Text,Tsukihi,0000,0000,0000,,Quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.62,0:23:59.97,Avoid Preview Text,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Does heat and beat refer to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.97,0:24:00.75,Avoid Preview Text,Tsukihi,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Karen-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.75,0:24:02.63,Avoid Preview Text,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,How should I pronounce the symbol that's used to represent "and"?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.63,0:24:04.76,Avoid Preview Text,Tsukihi,0000,0000,0000,,Understanding the text of the question is harder than understanding the question itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.76,0:24:06.53,Avoid Preview Text,Tsukihi,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Hitagi Crab Part Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.53,0:24:07.63,Avoid Preview Text,Tsukihi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll only show it to those who got it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.63,0:24:09.15,Avoid Preview Text,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,No one will get to see it...
